OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and warm with bright spells on
OL,7,FFriday, although some rain possible in
OL,8,Fthe evening. Dry, and warm over the
OL,9,Fweekend with bright spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
